channel.description:
US Nationalist News is Multi-Media Research, which started in June 2013.

Our YouTube page is used for Research into: Population Dynamics, Genetics, Crime, Demography, Philosophy, Psychology, Sociology, Aut/Syn Ecology, Anthropocentrism, Determinism versus Free will, Political Sciences, Game Theory, MiniMax, r/k Selection, Master-Slave morality, Kin Selection, Altruism — Hamilton's rule, Memetics, Darwinian Collective vs Egalitarianism, Collectivism versus Individualism, Christianity vs Naturalism, Meritocracy, Futurism, Utilitarianism, Functionalism (Class Collaboration) versus Conflict Theory (Class Struggle), and so on.
